'Cangjie programming language_api_std_collection_collection_ArrayList_get_set': 'When using Cangjie Code API, This example demonstrates how to use the get and set functions in the ArrayList class from the std.collection package.'

Code_Example:
import std.collection.*
main() {
    var list = ArrayList<Int64>([97, 100]) // list: [97, 100]
